item.title: Introduction
item.description: Abstract This study used COVID-19 database from Toronto Open Data Portal Gelfand (2020). We investigated the infection rate between age groups, and the source of infection. Part I: Introduction The Toronto Public Health department published data collected for COVID-19 to respond to the ongoing pandemic. Information contained in this dataset are extracted from the provincial communicable disease reporting system (iPHIS) and Torontoâ€™s custom COVID-19 case management system (CORES).
